==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Adjoining
<hw>Ad*join"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Joining to; contiguous;
adjacent; <as>as, an <ex>adjoining</ex> room</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The
<xex>adjoining</xex> fane.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Upon the hills <qex>adjoining</qex> to the city.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Adjacent; contiguous; near; neighboring;
abutting; bordering. See <er>Adjacent</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adjoint</ent>⟦br⟧
